text: I have always wanted to buy some furniture from Commune and this outlet at Tagore Lane just had a warehouse sale. Offering anything from pillows to sofas, you can find great deals for that modern furnishing that you have always dreamed off at a fraction of the original price.
The clearance items are cheap. Only retro style furnitures, so might not be for all.

My shopping experience at the warehouse was ruined by the lady (with curly hair) working on the laotop. When asked for prices, she rolled her eyes then proceed to search on her laptop. Her professionalism is highly questionable.
Great place to shop for modern rustic furniture.Good items does not come cheap
